- **Event mapping**: the Resolution section of `.brain/projects/wayfinder/research-pi-extension-event-semantics.svx` (your own findings: `.brain/projects/wayfinder/assets/pi-event-semantics-findings.svx`). Emit on `agent_settled`; cache `agent_end.messages` (+ latest `turn_end.turnIndex`); `turn_error` only for settled `stopReason: "error"`.
